{
  "uid": "log-pipeline-health",
  "title": "Log Pipeline Health (Phase 3C)",
  "timezone": "America/Chicago",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-6h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "editable": true,
  "tags": [
    "phase3c",
    "pipeline",
    "health",
    "alloy",
    "loki",
    "ingestion"
  ],
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Dashboard Purpose",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# Log Pipeline Health (Phase 3C)\n\nMonitors Alloy â†’ Loki log ingestion pipeline:\n- Data flow status by log source\n- Ingestion rates and volumes\n- Error rates in pipeline\n- Log source health (active vs dormant)\n\n**Data Sources**:\n- Loki log metadata (log_source label)\n- Error counts per source\n- Service identification quality (unknown_service ratio)\n\n**Use Case**: Detect pipeline failures, data loss, or ingestion issues"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Active Log Sources",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "count(count by (log_source) (count_over_time({log_source=~\".*\"}[5m]) > 0))"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "options": {
        "graphMode": "area",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "decimals": 0,
        "unit": "short"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total Logs (5m)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({log_source=~\".*\"}[5m]))"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Pipeline Errors (5m)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({level=\"error\"}[5m]))"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Unknown Service %",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "(sum(count_over_time({service_name=\"unknown_service\"}[5m])) / sum(count_over_time({log_source=~\".*\"}[5m])) * 100)"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 18,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Log Source Status (1h)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "topk(10, sum by (log_source) (count_over_time({log_source=~\".*\"}[1h])))",
          "format": "table"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Error Count by Source (1h)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "topk(10, sum by (log_source) (count_over_time({level=\"error\"}[1h])))",
          "format": "table"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 7,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Log Volume Trend by Source (6h)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (log_source) (rate(count_over_time({log_source=~\".*\"}[5m])[5m:1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ log_source }}"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 15,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 6
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "showLegend": true,
          "placement": "bottom"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Error Rate by Source (6h)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (log_source) (rate(count_over_time({level=\"error\"}[5m])[5m:1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ log_source }}"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 15,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 6
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "showLegend": true,
          "placement": "bottom"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
